{"tid":2194263,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"終於悟出股票必勝法","createTime":"2020-09-08T11:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T16:12:24.000Z","uid":272077,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"49f1c95532846610bc061bc885a49501d75d339a","tid":2194263,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於悟出股票必勝法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利用市場錯價, 把握內在價值&gt;價格的時候 <br />\n但這樣還不夠, 還要利用安全邊際和溢價去保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要有資產折讓和穩定的現金流 <br />\n業務要清晰, 易明, 簡潔和穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n管理層要誠實可靠和可信 <br />\n當然你要分清自己手持的是優質股, 還是劣質股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是優質股, 可以長線持有 <br />\n如果你去持有它, 一開始便沒有想手持十年以上的話, 那一開始便不要去想它 <br />\n金融市場長遠而言, 是weighing machine, 內在價值始終會最終被反映出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不需要理會短期的波動和波幅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n那麼多散戶在金融市場上輸錢, 就是因為太在意短期波動和波幅, 沒有耐心, 想一朝致富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就是因為散戶那麼沒有耐性和無知, 才令某些人必定成為贏家, 輸的機會係接近0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f718c0a5c5fc0a914ba14b43694a922982ae6758","tid":2194263,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:20:53.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n跟樓主呢套我賺左個首期番黎"},{"pid":"21cfbe674f57951dba28847e36462b4376f8bf99","tid":2194263,"uid":335538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"必勝法：<br />\n連登仔話買 &gt; 放貨<br />\n連登仔話放貨 &gt; 買"},{"pid":"bc848e7c956294a981084bfdac8dfc59ba471ea2","tid":2194263,"uid":162807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21cfbe674f57951db